<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0569b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b03">舍利弗發念致供而不念弟子者以其自有乞食法也</note>
<note n="0569b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b04">以雜食而發難端何異難求床坐者耶</note>
<note n="0569b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b05">文殊將顯淨名之德故以神力令眾會默然</note>
<note n="0569b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b06">恥字因前雜欲食而生既難之復耻之無非教也</note>
<note n="0569b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b07">諸佛菩薩問答欵敘情景楚楚一幅王摩詰畫也</note>
<note n="0569b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b08">攝身捨形而戒莫輕賤出世佛而談世間法也</note>
<note n="0569b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0569b09">彼國無王五百居士共治國政今言主眾所推也</note>
<note n="0570b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0570b01">飯施者利施也茲由戒定智慧等來則利施而兼法施矣所以毛孔皆出妙香也</note>
<note n="0570b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0570b02">孔聖無言之訓意亦如此</note>
<note n="0570b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0570b03">如來說法有三要一善行樂果軟善語也二惡行苦果剛強語也三讚善毀惡雜說也</note>
<note n="0570b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0570b04">世聞五刑三尺憲典彰彰亦欲範之入律乎</note>
<note n="0570b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0570b05">塵垢易增功德難是自非一心專求無以尅成具此八法終生淨土矣</note>
</p>
